    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>「本頁面說明中使用的素材，全部僅來自於體驗版。」</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/9767641730900e89c10dbf1bebafd324.avif?t=1758634083\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras_big/9767641730900e89c10dbf1bebafd324.avif?t=1758634083 width=800 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/c999579b5791142a78f49b2885275404.avif?t=1758634083\" width=600 height=270 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這個圖形看起來像六邊形嗎？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/e0e4aee19465ee221553bec676dd2eb1.poster.avif?t=1758634083\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/e0e4aee19465ee221553bec676dd2eb1.webm?t=1758634083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/e0e4aee19465ee221553bec676dd2eb1.mp4?t=1758634083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >當光線照射時，即可顯露原本的形態。<strong><br><br>「THANKS, LIGHT. - DEMO」</strong>精選了若干解謎關卡，讓任何人都能在本篇中快速上手THANKS, LIGHT.，並逐步體驗更有趣的謎題。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以嘗試第1章的一些關卡、故事的初期部分，以及尋找其中隱藏的要素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/53f13ecb96f13e2326455f3646f69fe1.webp?t=1758634083\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras_big/53f13ecb96f13e2326455f3646f69fe1.webp?t=1758634083 width=800 height=5 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/caf48c006c2512bc04deb77958eca819.avif?t=1758634083\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras_big/caf48c006c2512bc04deb77958eca819.avif?t=1758634083 width=800 height=147 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/66e39b5d348b86caa5ac5148129b2ab0.poster.avif?t=1758634083\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/66e39b5d348b86caa5ac5148129b2ab0.webm?t=1758634083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/66e39b5d348b86caa5ac5148129b2ab0.mp4?t=1758634083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>「THANKS, LIGHT - DEMO」</strong>是一款透過照射或吸收光線，讓物體在2D與3D狀態之間轉換的解謎平台遊戲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不要僅憑輪廓來判斷物體。請利用光線來確認物體的真實形態。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/53f13ecb96f13e2326455f3646f69fe1.webp?t=1758634083\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras_big/53f13ecb96f13e2326455f3646f69fe1.webp?t=1758634083 width=800 height=5 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/ec8873e16672f13ebe0ab9b0713e31d3.avif?t=1758634083\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras_big/ec8873e16672f13ebe0ab9b0713e31d3.avif?t=1758634083 width=800 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/3ffe1d03cf9d84060d1ccfe4d515b83b.poster.avif?t=1758634083\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/3ffe1d03cf9d84060d1ccfe4d515b83b.webm?t=1758634083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/3ffe1d03cf9d84060d1ccfe4d515b83b.mp4?t=1758634083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您知道即使是圓柱也可能存在方形嗎？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尋找每個圖形中隱藏的形狀，並以<strong>「THANKS, LIGHT - DEMO」</strong>獨特的方式解開部分謎題。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/53f13ecb96f13e2326455f3646f69fe1.webp?t=1758634083\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras_big/53f13ecb96f13e2326455f3646f69fe1.webp?t=1758634083 width=800 height=5 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/5aa27e02e02cce2762df935ecea53c75.avif?t=1758634083\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras_big/5aa27e02e02cce2762df935ecea53c75.avif?t=1758634083 width=800 height=151 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/87689ee34705ba6ef48e3e4bd303764e.poster.avif?t=1758634083\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/87689ee34705ba6ef48e3e4bd303764e.webm?t=1758634083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/87689ee34705ba6ef48e3e4bd303764e.mp4?t=1758634083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在2D狀態下沒有物理效果，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在3D狀態下則會套用物理。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >運用此特性，在二維與三維之間切換，挑戰各種物理謎題。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/53f13ecb96f13e2326455f3646f69fe1.webp?t=1758634083\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras_big/53f13ecb96f13e2326455f3646f69fe1.webp?t=1758634083 width=800 height=5 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/d3aa0620db993591600af2640c685e7f.avif?t=1758634083\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras_big/d3aa0620db993591600af2640c685e7f.avif?t=1758634083 width=800 height=222 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/c2d79308e41a0c240e7f82ad6420d35f.poster.avif?t=1758634083\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/c2d79308e41a0c240e7f82ad6420d35f.webm?t=1758634083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/c2d79308e41a0c240e7f82ad6420d35f.mp4?t=1758634083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在自稱「管理者」所準備的神祕空間中，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索並揭示隱藏的事件吧。</p>",
